  "text": "In our previous study, we identified imperatorin from Angelicae Dahuricae Radix [CITATION_1] , but the detailed mechanism for alleviating anti-inflammatory and anti-allergic effects in BMMC was not elucidated. The present study demonstrated that imperatorin suppressed degranulation and eicosanoid production, and these effects of imperatorin were mediated through the inhibition of 5-LO, cPLA2, MAPKs, PLCγ1, and NF-κB/IKK/ Akt activation in BMMC.",
